OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be dry with
OL,6,Fplenty of sunshine. Remaining dry this
OL,7,Fafternoon with some spells of sunshine
OL,8,Fbut some cloud spreading across from
OL,9,Fthe west at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will be dry and
OL,12,Fclear. Then the rest of the night will
OL,13,Fbe dry with lengthy clear spells. A
OL,14,Fcold night with a frost.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA mainly dry day with some
OL,17,Fbright spells across the north. More
OL,18,Fin the way of cloud across the south.
OL,19,FA mild day across northern Moray.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
